Package software.leonov.util.gson

Helper utilities, adapters, and factories for Google Gson.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GsonHelper
    A collection of static utility methods that simplify common serialization and deserialization operations using Google Gson.
    MultimapTypeAdapter<K,V>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Multimap values to and from JSON.
    MultimapTypeAdapterFactory
    Creates TypeAdapters for serializing and deserializing Multimap values to and from JSON.
    MultisetTypeAdapter<E>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Multiset values to and from JSON.
    MultisetTypeAdapterFactory
    Creates TypeAdapters for serializing and deserializing Multiset values to and from JSON.
    OptionalTypeAdapter<E>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Optional values to and from JSON.
    OptionalTypeAdapterFactory
    Creates TypeAdapters for serializing and deserializing Optional values to and from JSON.
    TableTypeAdapter<R,C,V>
    A TypeAdapter which can serialize and deserialize of Table values to and from JSON.
    TableTypeAdapterFactory
    Creates TypeAdapters for serializing and deserializing Table values to and from JSON.
